Package: IsoformVisRNA
Type: Package
Title: Isoform Visualizer for RNA-seq
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Nayeon", "Hyun", email = "nayeon.hyun@mail.utoronto.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Nayeon Hyun <nayeon.hyun@mail.utoronto.ca>
Description: Generate bar and box plots to compare expression ratios at the transcript-level.
    We expect input data to be transcript-level count matrices generated by kallisto.
